
## Exceptional Implementation Details
- The `ApiKeyManager` uses the IDE's credential store to securely manage API keys, ensuring that sensitive information is not exposed in the codebase.
- The `ReflectionUtils` class employs reflection to access private fields, which may be subject to change in future versions of the IDE, potentially leading to compatibility issues.

This documentation serves as a guide for developers and maintainers to understand the purpose and functionality of the Coding Aider Utilities module, as well as its integration points with other components of the system.
